{"tid":2247596,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憂國安離間12港人 削意志套料","createTime":"2020-10-18T03:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T03:50:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac8ddd68b080aed478a4e02b608bcebb13c0fc4","tid":2247596,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201018/C533C4EDRFGJFMDXEPWIUGFMI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201018%2FC533C4EDRFGJFMDXEPWIUGFMI4%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPfrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=b9792fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201018%2FC533C4EDRFGJFMDXEPWIUGFMI4%2F&h=d89aa920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201018/C533C4EDRFGJFMDXEPWIUGFMI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n憂國安離間12港人 削意志套料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hXhx-m61YffxFxOPz3mR5M2NOvM=/720x714/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I6JIT355FFBULMB2GHMITJWUME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhXhx-m61YffxFxOPz3mR5M2NOvM%3D%2F720x714%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI6JIT355FFBULMB2GHMITJWUME.jpg&h=ff396ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■通貝里昨在Twitter上載照片聲援12港人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12港人被送中逾月音訊全無，過去一年多在內地經歷被拘留、遭全天候監視的王鳳瑤以過來人身份指出，12港人面對的情況只會比她更為嚴峻，更指她在看守所期間，有被捕者被監禁三年或以上仍沒有機會與家人會面。她估計12港人除了可能被國安軟硬兼施套料、強行灌輸愛國教育外，更可能要面對國安用離間計分裂。她呼籲社會要繼續關注12港人。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆昨在記者會一開始便高舉「Save 12 HK Youths」標語。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾被內地羈留近一個半月的王婆婆不諱言，12名港青將難以得到外界幫助，「冇（人可以幫到佢哋）㗎，裏面係叫天不應，叫地不聞 」，「邊個可以幫到佢哋？佢（國安）唔會畀你聯絡到外面嘅人」。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n環保少女發文籲關注<br />\n<br />\n此外，關注氣候暖化議題的17歲瑞典環保少女通貝里（Greta Thunberg）昨在Twitter發文，參與社交網絡聲援12名被內地扣押港人的行動。她在白板寫上「#Save12HKYouths」，並邀請其他人參與行動。"},{"pid":"a1d86f401cb4bddd276250a1ff1ffbc2fa55c0de","tid":2247596,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T03:50:32.000Z","msg":"烤爹腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}